'''NGC 6946'''，也是所知的'''焰火星系 (Fireworks Galaxy)'''，'''Arp 29'''，和 '''[[科德韦尔深空天体表|Caldwell]] 12'''"，是個距離大約一千萬光年遠的[[中間螺旋星系|中間螺旋星系]]，位置界於[[仙王座|仙王座]]和[[天鵝座|天鵝座]]交界處，是[[威廉·赫歇爾|威廉·赫歇爾]]在1798年9月9日發現的。NGC 6946因為緊挨著[[銀道面|銀道面]]，因此受到[[銀河系|銀河系]]的[[星際物質|星際物質]]嚴重的遮蔽。在NGC 6946這個星系中已經發現了10顆[[超新星|超新星]]：[[SN_1917A|SN 1917A]]、[[SN_1939C|SN 1939C]]、SN 1948B、SN 1968D、SN 1969P、SN 1980K、SN 2002hh、SN 2004et、SN 2008S、和SN 2017eaw<ref>{{Cite web|title=ATel #10372: Confirmation of AT 2017eaw, a Probable Supernova in NGC 6946|url=http://www.astronomerstelegram.org/?read=10372|accessdate=2017-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626175220/http://www.astronomerstelegram.org/?read=10372|archive-date=2019-06-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=ATel #10376: Spectroscopic Classification of SN 2017eaw in NGC 6946 as a Young Type IIP Supernova|url=http://www.astronomerstelegram.org/?read=10376|accessdate=2017-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181122134023/http://www.astronomerstelegram.org/?read=10376|archive-date=2018-11-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="list">{{cite web|title=List of Supernovae|url=http://cbat.eps.harvard.edu/lists/Supernovae.html|accessdate=2010-07-12|publisher=Harvard-Smithsonian Center for Astrophysics (IAU)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170724193025/http://www.cbat.eps.harvard.edu/lists/Supernovae.html|archive-date=2017-07-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這使得它成為在100年內，這種類型事件最多產的已知星系。相比之下，[[銀河系|銀河系]]，恆星數量是NGC 6946的2倍，每個世紀卻只有一顆超新星的事件<ref>{{Cite web|title=Gemini Observatory Welcomes 2005 with Release of Galactic Fireworks Image|url=https://www.gemini.edu/node/116|access-date=2021-11-18|date=2005-01-01|work=Gemini Observatory|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220513223706/http://www.gemini.edu/node/116}}</ref>。它還擁有一顆{{link-en|失敗的超新星|failed supernova}}，形成潛在黑洞的[[N6946-BH1|N6946-BH1]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The search for failed supernovae with the Large Binocular Telescope: confirmation of a disappearing star|author=|url=https://academic.oup.com/mnras/article-lookup/doi/10.1093/mnras/stx816|last=Adams|first=S. M.|last2=Kochanek|first2=C. S.|date=2017-07|journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society|issue=4|doi=10.1093/mnras/stx816|volume=468|pages=4968–4981|language=en|arxiv=1609.01283v1|issn=0035-8711|last3=Gerke|first3=J. R.|last4=Stanek|first4=K. Z.|last5=Dai|first5=X.|access-date=2021-11-18|archive-date=2022-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220315001630/https://academic.oup.com/mnras/article-lookup/doi/10.1093/mnras/stx816}}</ref>。

